topic.title: Now Available: Thirty-two Foreign Relations Volumes
topic.body: These volumes are newly digitized as part of the Office's ongoing project, in partnership with the University of Wisconsin Digital Collections Center, to digitize the entire Foreign Relations series. They cover events that took place between 1920 and 1941 and were originally published in print between 1935 and 1943.
